Dialogue: 0,00:01:31.73,00:01:37.73,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:01:37.73,00:01:41.23,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｻｽｹ)フフフフ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:01:41.23,00:01:51.22,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.64,0:01:53.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Por especial...
Dialogue: 0,00:01:51.66,00:01:54.66,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾅﾙﾄ)特別って…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.34,0:01:59.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Por especial, quer dizer {\i1}isso aí{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,00:01:54.66,00:01:59.16,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,特別ってそれのことかよ！
Dialogue: 0,00:01:59.16,00:02:03.66,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,フフフフ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.65,0:02:05.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Acho que não vou perder.
Dialogue: 0,00:02:03.66,00:02:07.66,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,負ける気がしねえ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:02:07.66,00:02:10.16,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,カァ～！
Dialogue: 0,00:02:10.16,00:02:14.66,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:02:14.66,00:02:17.16,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,カァ～！
Dialogue: 0,00:02:17.16,00:02:27.15,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:02:36.66,00:02:38.66,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,なっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:02:38.66,00:02:48.65,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:02:58.59,00:03:07.09,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:03:07.09,00:03:08.59,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あっ！
Dialogue: 0,00:03:08.59,00:03:18.58,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:03:20.09,00:03:23.09,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ぐっ…あっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:03:23.09,00:03:33.08,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:42.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Sasuke, você...
Dialogue: 0,00:03:39.59,00:03:43.09,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,サスケ…お前…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:03:43.09,00:03:46.09,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:03:46.09,00:03:49.09,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,うっ！うっ…あぁ！
Dialogue: 0,00:03:49.09,00:03:51.03,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あぁ！
Dialogue: 0,00:03:51.03,00:03:53.03,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:55.94,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Se ficarem liberadas por muito tempo,
Dialogue: 0,00:03:53.03,00:03:56.03,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(左近)＜解放状態を長く続けていれば
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:58.92,Flashback,,0,0,0,,as Marcas da Maldição\Nprogressivamente comem seu corpo.
Dialogue: 0,00:03:56.03,00:03:59.03,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,徐々に体を呪印が侵食していく｡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:01.54,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Quando devoram você totalmente,
Dialogue: 0,00:03:59.03,00:04:01.53,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,侵食され尽くしたら…
Dialogue: 0,00:04:01.53,00:04:06.02,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,自分をなくすぜず～っとな…＞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:05.79,Flashback,,0,0,0,,você se perde para sempre.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:08.53,00:04:11.03,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,《この体…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.05,0:04:10.96,Italics,,0,0,0,,Este corpo...
Dialogue: 0,00:04:11.03,00:04:15.02,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ちんたらやってる時間はないようだな…》
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:14.83,Italics,,0,0,0,,Parece que não tenho\Ntempo a perder.
Dialogue: 0,00:04:20.03,00:04:22.02,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,うっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:04:23.53,00:04:27.52,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,《左手の感覚がねえ…》
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:27.24,Italics,,0,0,0,,Não sinto meu braço esquerdo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:32.54,Main,,0,0,0,,O poder que você tem
Dialogue: 0,00:04:30.03,00:04:32.52,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,お前のその力も…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:04:34.03,00:04:38.02,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,やはりリスクを伴うようだな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:38.18,Main,,0,0,0,,tem riscos para você também, não?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:43.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Você sabia?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:42.03,00:04:44.02,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,知ってるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:51.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Este lugar
Dialogue: 0,00:04:49.53,00:04:51.46,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ここは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:54.43,Main,,0,0,0,,é chamado "Vale do Fim".
Dialogue: 0,00:04:51.46,00:04:54.46,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,終末の谷と呼ばれている｡
Dialogue: 0,00:04:56.46,00:04:59.96,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ちょうどいい舞台じゃねえか｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.63,0:05:03.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Acho que é o palco perfeito.\NNão acha, Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,00:04:59.96,00:05:02.96,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,なぁナルト｡
Dialogue: 0,00:05:02.96,00:05:10.46,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:05:10.46,00:05:12.46,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あぁ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:14.44,Main,,0,0,0,,É mesmo...
Dialogue: 0,00:05:12.46,00:05:14.96,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,そうだったな｡
Dialogue: 0,00:05:14.96,00:05:19.46,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,おしゃべりはもう終わりだって言ったな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:18.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu disse que não falaria mais.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:19.46,00:05:22.96,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,じゃあそろそろしまいにしようぜ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:22.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Sendo assim, que tal\Ndarmos um fim a isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:25.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Nesta batalha.
Dialogue: 0,00:05:22.96,00:05:25.96,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,この戦いを…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:05:25.96,00:05:28.96,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,これまでの戦いを！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:28.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Todas nossas batalhas até agora!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:33.34,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Agora, time sete. Uzumaki Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,00:05:28.96,00:05:31.46,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｲﾙｶ)＜では次七班｡
Dialogue: 0,00:05:31.46,00:05:33.96,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,うずまきナルト＞＜あっ＞
Dialogue: 0,00:05:33.96,00:05:36.46,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｲﾙｶ)＜春野サクラ＞(ｻｸﾗ)＜あっ＞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:36.06,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Haruno Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,00:05:36.46,00:05:40.46,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜やった～！＞＜ナルトと一緒…＞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:38.52,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Isso aí!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.52,0:05:40.70,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Com o Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,00:05:40.46,00:05:42.96,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｲﾙｶ)＜そしてうちはサスケ＞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:42.57,Flashback,,0,0,0,,E o Uchiha Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:44.54,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Eba!
Dialogue: 0,00:05:42.96,00:05:46.96,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜やった～！＞＜サスケと一緒…＞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:46.81,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Com o Sasuke?
Dialogue: 0,00:05:46.96,00:05:50.89,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜せいぜい俺の足を引っ張るなよドベ＞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.21,0:05:50.75,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Tente não me atrapalhar, perdedor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:52.98,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Vocês...
Dialogue: 0,00:05:50.89,00:05:52.89,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)＜お前ら～！＞
Dialogue: 0,00:05:52.89,00:05:56.89,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜だって…だってだって！先生言ったってばよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.98,0:05:56.87,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Mas você falou...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:58.72,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Por isso eles...
Dialogue: 0,00:05:56.89,00:05:58.89,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,だからこいつは…＞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:06:01.69,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Não somos um trio?
Dialogue: 0,00:05:58.89,00:06:02.39,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜俺たちは三人一組なんだろ？＞
Dialogue: 0,00:06:02.39,00:06:06.39,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜そうよ私たち３人で１つなんだから！＞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:06.43,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Isso mesmo! Nós três somos um só!
Dialogue: 0,00:06:06.39,00:06:08.89,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜よう＞＜あっ…＞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:07.94,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,00:06:08.89,00:06:12.39,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜ケガはねえかよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:13.87,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Está ferido, gatinho assustado?
Dialogue: 0,00:06:12.39,00:06:14.39,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ビビリ君＞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:22.68,Flashback,,0,0,0,,E aí, está assustado? Gatinho ferido?
Dialogue: 0,00:06:15.89,00:06:20.39,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜よう…ケガはねえかよ？
Dialogue: 0,00:06:20.39,00:06:23.39,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ビビリ君＞
Dialogue: 0,00:06:23.39,00:06:26.39,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜俺はお前とも戦いたい＞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:26.35,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Você é alguém que quero enfrentar.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:26.39,00:06:28.39,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜あっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:06:28.39,00:06:31.39,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,サスケ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:30.53,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:36.06,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Quero enfrentar você também.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:31.39,00:06:36.39,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,俺もお前と戦いたい！＞
Dialogue: 0,00:06:36.39,00:06:39.89,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜もう俺の目の前で
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.53,0:06:40.06,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Não quero ver mais mortes
Dialogue: 0,00:06:39.89,00:06:43.89,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,大切な仲間が死ぬのは見たくない＞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:44.23,Flashback,,0,0,0,,de meus preciosos companheiros!
Dialogue: 0,00:06:43.89,00:06:46.39,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜口寄せの術！＞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:45.90,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Jutsu de Invocação!
Dialogue: 0,00:06:46.39,00:06:51.33,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:06:51.33,00:06:53.83,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜サクラちゃんは…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:56.31,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Eu vou proteger a Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,00:06:53.83,00:06:56.33,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,俺が守る！＞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:57.79,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Qual é a graça?
Dialogue: 0,00:06:56.33,00:06:59.83,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜何がおかしい？＞＜おかしいんじゃねえってばよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.79,0:07:01.33,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Não tem graça! Eu estou feliz!
Dialogue: 0,00:06:59.83,00:07:01.83,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,うれしいんだよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.78,0:07:05.75,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Fico feliz em pensar que\Nfinalmente posso derrotá-lo aqui.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:01.83,00:07:05.83,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,お前にここでやっと勝てると思ったらな＞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:09.72,Flashback,,0,0,0,,O que você disse?\NPare com essas bobagens, perdedor!
Dialogue: 0,00:07:05.83,00:07:09.83,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜んだと…落ちこぼれがほざいてんなよ！＞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:13.69,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Não vou ser um perdedor para sempre!
Dialogue: 0,00:07:09.83,00:07:13.83,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜いつまでも落ちこぼれの足手まといじゃねえぜ！＞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.69,0:07:15.34,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Venha para cima.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:13.83,00:07:17.33,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜さっさと来い＞＜その前に額当てをしろ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:18.50,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Coloque sua bandana\Nantes. Eu espero.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:17.33,00:07:20.83,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,待ってやる＞＜いらねえよそんなもんは＞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:20.67,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Não preciso dela.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:22.87,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Vamos logo!
Dialogue: 0,00:07:20.83,00:07:24.33,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜いいからしろ！＞
Dialogue: 0,00:07:24.33,00:07:26.83,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜お前は俺の額に
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:29.84,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Você sequer vai conseguir\Narranhar minha testa.
Dialogue: 0,00:07:26.83,00:07:30.33,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,傷一つ付けることすらできやしない＞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:31.49,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Você está errado!
Dialogue: 0,00:07:30.33,00:07:33.33,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜違う！これは木ノ葉の忍として
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:33.73,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Falo sobre a badana como garantia
Dialogue: 0,00:07:33.33,00:07:36.33,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,対等に戦う証しだって言ってんだよ！＞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:36.42,Flashback,,0,0,0,,de que estamos lutando de igual\Npara igual como ninjas da Vila da Folha!
Dialogue: 0,00:07:36.33,00:07:38.33,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜ナルト～！＞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:38.39,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,00:07:38.33,00:07:40.33,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜サスケ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:40.35,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,00:07:40.33,00:07:44.33,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,絶対勝つ！＞＜いい気になってんじゃねえ！＞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.35,0:07:42.14,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Eu vou vencer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:44.32,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Não me subestime!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:47.27,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Parem!
Dialogue: 0,00:07:44.33,00:07:46.82,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜やめてよ～！＞
Dialogue: 0,00:07:50.76,00:07:53.26,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,そしてこれからは…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:53.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Daí em diante...
Dialogue: 0,00:08:04.76,00:08:06.76,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,《千鳥！》
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:07.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Chidori!
Dialogue: 0,00:08:17.76,00:08:19.76,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,《螺旋丸！》
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:19.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Rasengan!
Dialogue: 0,00:08:24.68,00:08:26.68,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,螺旋丸‼千鳥‼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:49.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Rasengan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:49.70,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chidori!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:49.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chidori!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:49.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Rasengan!
Dialogue: 0,00:08:48.21,00:08:50.20,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,螺旋丸‼千鳥‼
Dialogue: 0,00:09:00.71,00:09:02.20,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,うっ！
Dialogue: 0,00:09:14.71,00:09:16.70,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.65,0:09:20.72,Italics,,0,0,0,,Esse Chakra...
Dialogue: 0,00:09:18.71,00:09:21.21,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)《このチャクラは…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:09:21.21,00:09:23.20,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,マズい！》
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:23.00,Italics,,0,0,0,,Isso não é bom!
Dialogue: 0,00:09:44.71,00:09:46.70,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(雷鳴)
Dialogue: 0,00:09:50.21,00:09:52.20,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(雷鳴)
Dialogue: 0,00:10:34.64,00:10:44.63,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:10:54.64,00:11:04.63,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:11:14.64,00:11:24.63,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:11:34.57,00:11:44.56,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:11:54.57,00:12:04.56,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:12:14.57,00:12:24.56,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:42.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,00:12:41.01,00:12:43.00,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ナルト…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:56.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu...
Dialogue: 0,00:12:55.01,00:12:57.00,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,俺は…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:13:27.44,00:13:29.94,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,うっ！あぁ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:13:59.94,00:14:01.94,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)雨だ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:03.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Começou a chover...\NIsso vai apagar o cheiro?
Dialogue: 0,00:14:01.94,00:14:03.94,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,においは消えていないか？
Dialogue: 0,00:14:03.94,00:14:08.43,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾟｯｸﾝ)大丈夫だ近いぞこっちだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.13,0:14:06.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Sem problemas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.01,0:14:08.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Já estamos perto. Por aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.28,0:14:22.37,Italics,,0,0,0,,Cheguei tarde demais?
Dialogue: 0,00:14:20.37,00:14:22.37,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)遅かったか…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.23,0:14:32.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,00:14:30.37,00:14:32.37,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾟｯｸﾝ)ナルト…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.74,0:14:39.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Como as coisas acabaram assim?
Dialogue: 0,00:14:36.87,00:14:39.37,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾟｯｸﾝ)何でこんなことに…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:14:44.87,00:14:48.37,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(においを嗅ぐ音)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.55,0:14:51.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Isto é do Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,00:14:49.87,00:14:51.87,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,サスケのだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:34.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Não cheguei a tempo...\NPor favor, me perdoe.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:29.81,00:15:32.81,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)間に合わなくて
Dialogue: 0,00:15:32.81,00:15:35.30,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,すまなかったな…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:15:40.31,00:15:42.81,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)ナルト…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.70,0:15:42.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,00:15:42.81,00:15:45.81,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,お前のことだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.57,0:15:45.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu sei que tipo de pessoa você é...
Dialogue: 0,00:15:45.81,00:15:48.30,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,必死だったんだろう…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:48.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Você deve ter se esforçado\Ndesesperadamente.
Dialogue: 0,00:15:54.31,00:15:56.81,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)《サスケ…》
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:15:56.46,Italics,,0,0,0,,Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,00:15:56.81,00:16:04.30,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(足音)
Dialogue: 0,00:16:13.31,00:16:19.74,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:22.34,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Esse é meu garoto.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:19.74,00:16:22.74,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾌｶﾞｸ)＜さすが俺の子だ＞
Dialogue: 0,00:16:22.74,00:16:32.73,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:39.06,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Quando está sozinho comigo,\Nseu pai só fala de você.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:34.74,00:16:39.24,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾐｺﾄ)＜私といるときはあなたのことばかり話してるのよ父さん＞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:42.23,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Você é meu único irmão.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:39.24,00:16:42.24,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｲﾀﾁ)＜お前と俺は唯一無二の兄弟だ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:47.73,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Continuarei a ser um\Nobstáculo para você superar.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:42.24,00:16:44.74,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,お前の越えるべき壁として
Dialogue: 0,00:16:44.74,00:16:48.24,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,俺はお前と共にあり続けるのさ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:16:48.24,00:16:51.24,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,たとえ憎まれようともな＞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.84,0:16:51.20,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Mesmo que você me odeie...
Dialogue: 0,00:16:51.24,00:16:53.74,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:58.96,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Você é alguém que pode conseguir\No Mangekyo Sharingan, como eu.
Dialogue: 0,00:16:53.74,00:16:57.24,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜お前も俺と同じ万華鏡写輪眼を
Dialogue: 0,00:16:57.24,00:16:59.24,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,開眼しうる者だ＞
Dialogue: 0,00:16:59.24,00:17:01.24,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:17:01.24,00:17:04.74,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｲﾀﾁ)＜ただしそれには条件がある＞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:04.65,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Mas há uma condição.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:04.74,00:17:10.24,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:17:10.24,00:17:13.24,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜最も親しい友を…＞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.49,0:17:13.46,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Seu melhor amigo...
Dialogue: 0,00:17:13.24,00:17:23.23,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:17:25.17,00:17:27.17,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾟｯｸﾝ)終末の谷｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:27.49,Main,,0,0,0,,O Vale do Fim...
Dialogue: 0,00:17:27.17,00:17:31.17,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,こんな所でサスケとナルトが戦うとはな…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.49,0:17:31.04,Main,,0,0,0,,E pensar que eles\Ndois batalhariam aqui...
Dialogue: 0,00:17:31.17,00:17:34.17,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:17:34.17,00:17:36.67,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,皮肉なもんだな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:36.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Que irônico.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:36.67,00:17:38.67,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:17:38.67,00:17:40.67,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)ああ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:40.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:40.67,00:17:43.17,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:17:43.17,00:17:45.67,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)この流れを見ていると
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.39,0:17:45.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Quando olho esse fluxo de água,
Dialogue: 0,00:17:45.67,00:17:50.17,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,まるで永遠に止まることなく流れ続いていく戦いを
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.93,0:17:52.91,Main,,0,0,0,,é como se fosse sido confrontado\Npor uma batalha eterna e sem fim.
Dialogue: 0,00:17:50.17,00:17:52.67,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,見せつけられているようだ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:17:52.67,00:17:56.17,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:17:56.17,00:18:00.17,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)木ノ葉の里を作ったこの像の２人の運命と
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:59.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Como o destino das duas\Npessoas nessas estátuas,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:02.55,Main,,0,0,0,,os fundadores da Vila da Folha.
Dialogue: 0,00:18:00.17,00:18:02.17,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,同じように…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:18:02.17,00:18:06.67,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:18:06.67,00:18:09.67,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)ナルトとサスケ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:13.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Naruto e Sasuke, desde\Nque estejam vivos...
Dialogue: 0,00:18:09.67,00:18:13.67,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,この２人の命があるかぎりな｡
Dialogue: 0,00:18:15.17,00:18:17.11,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)あっ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:18:17.11,00:18:27.10,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.10,0:18:35.15,Flashback,,0,0,0,,Você terá que matar
Dialogue: 0,00:18:32.11,00:18:35.10,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,＜最も親しい友を…＞
Dialogue: 0,00:18:37.11,00:18:39.60,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｲﾀﾁ)＜殺すことだ＞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.21,0:18:39.81,Flashback,,0,0,0,,o seu melhor amigo!
Dialogue: 0,00:18:53.61,00:18:56.11,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,《俺は…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:55.91,Italics,,0,0,0,,Eu não vou...
Dialogue: 0,00:18:56.11,00:18:59.60,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あんたの言いなりにはならない！》
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.83,0:18:59.91,Italics,,0,0,0,,...seguir tudo que você diz!
Dialogue: 0,00:19:06.61,00:19:11.11,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,《俺は俺のやり方で力を手に入れる｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.07,0:19:11.08,Italics,,0,0,0,,Vou conseguir poder\Ndo meu próprio jeito!
Dialogue: 0,00:19:11.11,00:19:16.61,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,俺は俺のやり方であんたを超える！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:16.30,Italics,,0,0,0,,Vou superá-lo do meu jeito!
Dialogue: 0,00:19:16.61,00:19:19.10,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,必ずな！》
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.95,0:19:18.89,Italics,,0,0,0,,Sem dúvidas!
Dialogue: 0,00:19:32.11,00:19:36.11,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)雨やんだな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:35.98,Main,,0,0,0,,A chuva parou?
Dialogue: 0,00:19:36.11,00:19:38.60,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾟｯｸﾝ)うん…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:38.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim...
Dialogue: 0,00:19:53.61,00:19:58.61,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,あの雨だもうにおいじゃ追えねえ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:55.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Depois de toda essa chuva,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.80,0:19:58.30,Main,,0,0,0,,não vou mais conseguir\Nseguir o cheiro.
Dialogue: 0,00:19:58.61,00:20:03.61,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,それにサスケを追うよりナルトが先だ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:02.74,Main,,0,0,0,,O Naruto é mais importante\Nque perseguir o Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:03.61,00:20:05.60,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(ｶｶｼ)ああ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.13,0:20:05.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,00:20:27.04,00:20:29.54,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(男１)フフ…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:20:29.54,00:20:33.54,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,オモシロイコトニナッテキタダロ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:33.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Ficou interessante, hein?
Dialogue: 0,00:20:33.54,00:20:35.54,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,(男２)うん｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:35.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim...
Dialogue: 0,00:21:17.44,00:21:21.44,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬(ｴﾝﾃﾞｨﾝｸﾞﾃｰﾏ)
Dialogue: 0,00:21:21.44,00:21:26.44,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬一つ一つ思い出せば
Dialogue: 0,00:21:26.44,00:21:32.44,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬全てわかっていた気がしていたのに
Dialogue: 0,00:21:32.44,00:21:37.44,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬色褪せた言葉は
Dialogue: 0,00:21:37.44,00:21:43.87,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬僕のすぐそばに置いてあった
Dialogue: 0,00:21:43.87,00:21:48.87,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬答えの出ない夜と
Dialogue: 0,00:21:48.87,00:21:54.37,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬一片の温もりと
Dialogue: 0,00:21:54.37,00:21:59.87,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬遥か彼方の憧れと
Dialogue: 0,00:21:59.87,00:22:02.87,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬ただそれだけを
Dialogue: 0,00:22:02.87,00:22:08.87,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬繰り返し僕は生きている
Dialogue: 0,00:22:08.87,00:22:11.37,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:22:11.37,00:22:17.87,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬この両手に抱えているもの
Dialogue: 0,00:22:17.87,00:22:21.87,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬時のしずく
Dialogue: 0,00:22:21.87,00:22:28.37,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬そっと握り締めて忘れた記憶
Dialogue: 0,00:22:28.37,00:22:31.37,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬失くした言葉
Dialogue: 0,00:22:31.37,00:22:39.87,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬～
Dialogue: 0,00:22:39.87,00:22:44.37,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,♬この思いは
Dialogue: 0,00:22:46.80,00:22:49.80,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,〈ごめん…ホントに…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:22:49.80,00:22:52.31,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,ごめんなサクラちゃん…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:22:52.31,00:22:54.80,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,俺サスケを連れて帰るって
Dialogue: 0,00:22:54.80,00:22:58.31,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,一生の約束だって言ったのにな…｡
Dialogue: 0,00:22:58.31,00:23:01.80,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,けどよまだ終わっちゃいねえってばよ｡
Dialogue: 0,00:23:01.80,00:23:05.80,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,約束は絶対守る！俺ってばいつも言ってたからな｡
Dialogue: 0,00:23:05.80,00:23:11.30,JPN TOP,,0,0,0,,自分のことばは曲げねえそれが俺の忍道だからよ〉
